      <title>韩国敦促 Telegram 严厉打击 Deepfake 性犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/south-korea-urges-telegram-to-crack-down-on-deepfake-sex-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于此类内容激增，韩国政府已要求通讯应用程序 Telegram 和其他社交媒体公司从其平台上删除露骨的深度伪造性爱图片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/south-korea-urges-telegram-to-crack-down-on-deepfake-sex-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:54:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美团外卖销售额超出预期，食品外卖需求强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/meituan-s-sales-beat-estimates-on-strong-food-delivery-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其核心食品配送业务扩张之后，美团的季度营收超出预期，这向越来越担心国内消费疲软的投资者发出了积极信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/meituan-s-sales-beat-estimates-on-strong-food-delivery-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:45:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据盗窃激增，德国企业成本一年达 2670 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/german-firms-costs-hit-267-billion-in-year-as-data-theft-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据科技游说团体 Bitkom 的一项调查，过去一年，超过 80% 的德国公司成为数据盗窃、工业间谍或破坏的受害者，造成的累计损失增加近三分之一，达到创纪录的 2670 亿欧元（2980 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/german-firms-costs-hit-267-billion-in-year-as-data-theft-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乐高 CEO 希望通过更多游戏交易复制《堡垒之夜》的成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/lego-ceo-wants-to-copy-fortnite-success-with-more-game-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乐高首席执行官表示，乐高公司与 Epic Games 合作推出的《堡垒之夜》大获成功，自推出以来已覆盖 8300 万人，该公司目前正在寻求新的数字合作伙伴关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/lego-ceo-wants-to-copy-fortnite-success-with-more-game-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BCG 称印度银行在网络安全支出方面落后于全球同行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/indian-lenders-lag-global-peers-on-cybersecurity-spends-bcg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿咨询集团董事总经理兼合伙人 Neetu Chitkara 表示，网络盗窃和欺诈案件不断增加，将迫使在网络安全支出方面已经落后于全球同行的印度银行加大力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/indian-lenders-lag-global-peers-on-cybersecurity-spends-bcg</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 06:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆克什·安巴尼预计将在年度股东大会上提供有关 Reliance Jio 和零售业 IPO 的详细信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/ambani-s-reliance-agm-may-offer-clues-on-reliance-jio-reliance-retail-ipos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当亚洲首富穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 于周四发表备受期待的年度公开演讲时，信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 的股东们将会仔细分析他的讲话，以了解其电信和零售巨头上市的具体细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/ambani-s-reliance-agm-may-offer-clues-on-reliance-jio-reliance-retail-ipos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 04:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国空军将用瑞典战斗机取代老式 F-16</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/thai-air-force-to-replace-old-f-16s-with-swedish-fighter-jets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据泰国皇家空军周二发表的声明称，泰国皇家空军将购买一定数量的瑞典鹰狮战斗机，以取代其老化的美国制造的 F-16 机队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/thai-air-force-to-replace-old-f-16s-with-swedish-fighter-jets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果因业务重点转变削减在线服务部门职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/apple-cuts-about-100-services-jobs-as-part-of-priority-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司采取罕见举措，在其数字服务部门裁员约 100 人，这是该关键部门工作重点转变的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/apple-cuts-about-100-services-jobs-as-part-of-priority-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利三菱日联金融集团和花旗集团上调目标价 乐天股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/rakuten-surges-as-morgan-stanley-mufg-citi-raise-price-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利三菱日联证券等券商因乐天集团移动业务的成功而上调其目标价，此后，乐天集团股价攀升至 2022 年 4 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/rakuten-surges-as-morgan-stanley-mufg-citi-raise-price-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼加入日本涨价潮，将 PlayStation 价格上调 19%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/sony-hikes-playstation-5-price-in-japan-citing-cost-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索尼集团公司 (Sony Group Corp.) 在日本将其主打游戏机的价格上调约 19%，至近 550 美元，这是亚洲第二大经济体走出通货紧缩周期的最显著迹象之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/sony-hikes-playstation-5-price-in-japan-citing-cost-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 08:21:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
